Body:

Title: b'Multiple H1 headings'
Body:
b'![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/44382025/93749681-3b134f00-fbf2-11ea-9011-046c37e19b71.png)

I understand that the top h1 needs to be there for the title of the document and the  H1 at the bottom of the page needs to be there for the chapter heading. 

Is there any way around this?  '
